snippet.title: Official Trailer for The Paper Arcade
snippet.description:
This is a growing collection of games that I began creating as far back as 2008 that I decided to release on Steam.

Grab the Demo, Wishlist and/or Buy today:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2381810/The_Paper_Arcade/

You’ll find a slew of different retro games with a unique twist. ---
